						<p><hi rend="italic">Fragment of stone built into the wall (inner-side), left of entrance into the raṅga-maṇḍapa of the Śaṅkaraliṅga temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>13th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">13th Century A.D.,</hi> seems to register a gift of toll incomes on certain articles of merchandise.</p>						

